sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist<br/>(Notebook / Pipeline)
    participant Exp as AI4RAGExperiment<br/>Orchestrator
    participant SS as SearchSpace<br/>Parameter Manager
    participant MPS as ModelsPreSelector<br/>(Optional)
    participant HPO as GAMOptimizer<br/>Surrogate HPO
    participant Chunker as LangChainChunker<br/>Text Splitting
    participant Embed as EmbeddingModel<br/>(LS / OpenAI)
    participant VS as VectorStore<br/>(LS / Chroma)
    participant Retriever as Retriever<br/>Vector/Hybrid Search
    participant FM as FoundationModel<br/>(LS / OpenAI)
    participant Eval as UnitxtEvaluator<br/>Metrics
    participant LS as Llama Stack Server<br/>Configurable Port<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant EH as EventHandler<br/>(Local / KFP)

    Note over User, EH: Flow 1: RAG Optimization Experiment

    User->>Exp: search(rag_template, search_space,<br/>benchmark_data, n_iterations)

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Exp, LS: Optional: Models Pre-Selection Phase
        Exp->>MPS: pre_select(search_space)
        MPS->>LS: GET /models (models.list)<br/>API Key (Bearer)
        LS-->>MPS: Available models list
        loop For each model pair
            MPS->>Embed: embed(benchmark_docs)
            Embed->>LS: POST /embeddings<br/>API Key (Bearer)
            LS-->>Embed: Embedding vectors
            MPS->>VS: insert(chunks, embeddings)
            MPS->>FM: chat(prompt + context)
            FM->>LS: POST /chat/completions<br/>API Key (Bearer)
            LS-->>FM: Generated answer
            MPS->>Eval: evaluate(answer, ground_truth)
            Eval-->>MPS: Metrics (correctness, faithfulness)
        end
        MPS-->>Exp: Top-N model pairs
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Exp, EH: Main Optimization Loop (n_iterations)
        loop For each iteration
            Exp->>HPO: suggest_next_params()
            HPO->>SS: sample(constraints)
            SS-->>HPO: Valid parameter set
            HPO-->>Exp: Next hyperparameters<br/>(chunk_size, overlap, model, search_mode, ...)

            Note over Exp, VS: RAG Pipeline Execution
            Exp->>Chunker: chunk(documents, chunk_size, overlap)
            Chunker-->>Exp: Document chunks

            Exp->>Embed: embed(chunks)
            Embed->>LS: POST /embeddings<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, API Key
            LS-->>Embed: Embedding vectors
            Embed-->>Exp: Embedded chunks

            Exp->>VS: insert(chunks, embeddings)
            VS->>LS: POST /vector_io/insert<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, API Key
            LS-->>VS: Confirmation

            Exp->>Retriever: retrieve(query, top_k)
            Retriever->>VS: query(embedding, top_k)
            VS->>LS: POST /vector_io/query<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, API Key
            LS-->>VS: Similar chunks
            VS-->>Retriever: Retrieved context
            Retriever-->>Exp: Relevant chunks

            Exp->>FM: chat(prompt + context)
            FM->>LS: POST /chat/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, API Key
            LS-->>FM: Generated answer
            FM-->>Exp: RAG answer

            Note over Exp, Eval: Evaluation
            Exp->>Eval: evaluate(answer, ground_truth)
            Eval-->>Exp: Metrics with confidence intervals<br/>(answer_correctness, faithfulness,<br/>context_correctness)

            Exp->>HPO: update(params, score)
            Note over HPO: GAM surrogate model updated

            Exp->>EH: emit(iteration_results)
            EH-->>Exp: Event recorded<br/>(JSON file or KFP metadata)
        end
    end

    Exp-->>User: Optimal RAG Pattern<br/>(best hyperparameters + metrics)
